The world shaking rucuss of the Titans had even hit The Realm of Light, far in the eastern sky.<br>
Earlier he had gotten a vision of there being trouble going on in Hades. Apollo rubbed his chin in thought, maybe Uncle Hades was in need of some assistance?<br>
<br>
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br>
<br>
In a flash of golden light Apollo appeared in Hades, his strong glow pushing back the shadows to the innermost recesses of Hades as he walked down the halls of his Uncle's palatial abode.<br>
His midnight blue toga dragged on the floor as he came up to two guards at the face of Hades' throne room. The guards bowed to Apollo and let him pass.<br>
<br>
His azue eyes bounced around the throne room, to find no one. His eyes glazed over golden as he recieved a vision, of Hades and Persephone in the garden. He quickly began to scurry in the direction of the beautiful garden.<br>
