<br>
&quot;The situation has been taken care of and resolved.  The Titans tried to break free from their prison.  The Chains of Hephaestus gave way.  New chains have been placed on the doors.  The Titans will never escape those doors.  Not if I have anything to say about it.  Now if you'll excuse me...I have my wife to attend to...&quot;<br>
<br>
::Hades nodded again to the young Apollo, before turning around and began heading towards his wife, whom he just left:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/upersephoneqofu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 98<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(10/28/01 7:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=181.topic&index=39>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.chooseindia.com/starworld/aishwarya3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the nightmares</span><hr size=1> ::After a few moments, Persephone falls back asleep. Soft pleasant dreams flow through her head, making her smile softly. Then dark nightmares begins to pour through her head making her whimper and cry out in her sleep. Begins to toss and turn in her soft cushioned chair violently. Wakes up with her eyes bulged out and frantic with a loud bloody scream that is heard throughout the palace. Begins to call out his name::<br>
