&quot;Yes, ofcourse, she probably needs you...&quot; he said quickly turning around in a huff.<br>
<br>
He crossed his arms as he walked down the hall.<br>
<br>
&quot;Well you know what whatever, I don't know why I even came to help. Not like he ever needs any.&quot; he rolled his eyes.<br>
<br>
&quot;Old people are SO weird!&quot; he screamed before fading away in a flash of soft golden light. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=181.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=181.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessageRange?topicID=181.topic&start=61&stop=61>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=181.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=181.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=181.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=181.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=181.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=181.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=181.topic>